Title: Dalong's Brocade and Indigo
---
Raisedï¼š

A monk ask Dalong (Great Dragon), "The color-body
(rupakaya) falls to ruin. So what is the firm and stable Dharmabody?"

Long said, "The mountain flowers open,
resembling brocade

The valley river deep,
like indigo."
